    "en": {
      "title": "Yellow-blue gas surrounds Galle Cricket Ground",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "People lined up today (28) at the Galle International Cricket Ground with litro and Laugfs gas cylinders for the Test cricket match between Australia and Sri Lanka which starts tomorrow (29).",
        "The queues are unfamiliar to Australian cricketers and spectators, so they ask Sri Lankans, including Sri Lankan players.",
        "The photo shows gas consumers queuing around the Galle International Cricket Stadium with gas cylinders."
      ],
